extends ../_layouts/docs

block title
  title Billing | BitPay

append vars
  -var pageSelected = 'Docs'
  -var subpageSelected = 'Email Billing'

block information
  h2.header__bottom-border-left Billing
  p.lead BitPay merchants can use our bitcoin billing tools to invoice and receive payment with all of the ease of sending an email.

  h3 Email Invoices
  p Send bitcoin invoices to your clients via email on a one-time or recurring basis. Just enter your preferences and billing information in the <a href="/dashboard/merchant/client-billing">simple form</a> on your merchant dashboard and click once to generate and send a bill.

  h3 Plug-Ins and Integrations
  p We've built our bitcoin invoicing solutions into several popular billing services and plug-ins. Find all of our integrated solutions <a href="/integrations">here</a>. All you need is a <a href="/dashboard/signup">BitPay account</a> to get started.
